      <item>
        <title>Unlock Nokia 3 Bootloader</title>
        <description>&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Enable developer options&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Enable OEM Unlocking (OEM Unlock)&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Enable USB debugging mode&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Change default USB configuration, choose File Transfer (MTP)&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Install adb and fastboot (&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;sudo apt-get install android-tools-adb android-tools-fastboot&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Install nokia usb drive&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Connect your phone to your PC and approve all usb connection&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;adb devices&lt;/code&gt;, then it will show the serial number&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;adb reboot bootloader&lt;/code&gt;, then your devices will boot into fastboot mode&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;fastboot devices&lt;/code&gt;, to make sure that your device still connected to your PC and it will show your phone serial number&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;fastboot oem key $(echo -n &quot;YOUR_PHONE_SERIAL_NUMBER&quot; | md5sum | tr [a-z] [A-Z])&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;fastboot flashing unlock&lt;/code&gt;, your phone will ask you about unlocking bootloader&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Press vol up (yes)&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
